## customNN-driven mixbeat example.
##
## The custom02 envelope creates short windows where the embedded-beat
## effect becomes strong, instead of applying mixbeat continuously.
##
## Assumes you run from the repo root:
##   sbagenx -D examples/X/custom-mixbeat-windowed.sbg
##   sbagenx examples/X/custom-mixbeat-windowed.sbg

-m assets/river1.ogg

custom02: e=0 0 0 0 1 1 0 0 0

windowed: mix/70 custom02:mixbeat:5.5/40 200+5.5/18

00:00 windowed
00:10:00 windowed
